  "title": "PROCUREMENT/PURCHASING MANAGER",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Description </strong><br /><br />- In charge of overall strategy and planning of our procurement process  </p><p>-Monitor and control of purchasing and ordering of the provisions such as rice, spices, canned Food from India and Southeast Asia Region.</p><p>-Co-ordinates and liaise with suppliers and wholesalers.</p><p>-Develop and maintain our stocks and inventory control in the computer system.<br /><br />-Sales promotion and marketing.</p><p>-Expand local market and maintain existing customers.</p><p>-Supervise retail service staff.</p><p><br /><strong>Job Requirements</strong></p><p>- Ready to work any shift.</p><p>- Need to work long term.</p><p>- Ready to work for Public holidays & Sunday.</p>",
